            "id": 6408651,
            "title": "盤中速報 - 啟碁(6285)股價拉至漲停，漲停價197.0元，成交22,242張",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>啟碁(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6285:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6285\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6285-TW</a>)07日09:34上漲17.5元，股價漲停報197.0元，委買96張、委賣4,824張，成交22,242張。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>主要業務為衛星通訊系列產品。移動與攜帶產品之通訊系列產品。上述產品相關之進出口貿易業務。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>啟碁(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6285:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6285\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6285-TW</a>)近5日股價上漲0.28%，集中市場<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/TWS/TSE01\">加權指數</a>上漲0.17%，股價波動與大盤表現同步。</p></section><section><p><em>近5日籌碼</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>三大法人合計買賣超：+5,827 張</li> <li>外資買賣超：+4,087 張</li> <li>投信買賣超：+1,488 張</li> <li>自營商買賣超：+252 張</li> <li>融資增減：-1,932 張</li> <li>融券增減：+57 張</li> </ul></section></main>",
            "link": "https://news.cnyes.com/news/id/6408651",
